# ── Version control ──────────────────────────────────────────────
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes

# ── Dependencies (rebuilt inside Docker) ─────────────────────────
**/node_modules

# ── Next.js build artifacts (rebuilt inside Docker) ──────────────
**/.next
**/out

# ── Coverage / test output ────────────────────────────────────────
**/coverage

# ── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*

# ── Environment files (secrets — never bake into images) ─────────
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.development
**/.env.production
# Keep examples (.env.example) — they have no real secrets
!**/.env.example

# ── IDE / OS noise ───────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode
.idea
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# ── Docs (not needed at runtime) ─────────────────────────────────
**/README.md
**/AGENTS.md
**/CLAUDE.md

# ── Windows-only helpers (not needed in Linux container) ─────────
start.bat
